RawLine: ITEM_04520_Tip,能讓人氣息順暢的藥，曾有人服用此藥後在水中待了一個時辰，上岸後仍精神奕奕。不過這藥好像有點不對勁......,能让人气息顺畅的药，曾有人服用此药后在水中待了一个时辰，上岸后仍精神奕奕。不过这药好像有点不对劲......

Items.mt: It is a medicine that can make people's breath flow smoothly, and some people once stayed in the water for an hour after taking this medicine, and they were still in good spirits after coming back to shore. But this drug seems to be a bit off ......
